data.description: Incredible single level home on a huge lot with a pebble-tec pool! This home has been meticulously cared for and boasts a split floor plan with 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, den, formal living, dining room, huge great room and oversized 3 car garage! The kitchen features granite countertops, a new stainless steel stove, new microwave, new dishwasher, and a new RO system that feeds into the refrigerator and the sink! And there's more...the HVAC is only 4 months old  and the tile floors were recently stripped and resealed! The sparkling pool was drained and media blasted last summer, and the new 6x8 shed will convey with the sale! The desert landscaping is not only beautiful but low maintenance. Come see this home today because this one won't last!
